iSES is a sponsored meeting of the Technical Committee on VLSI, IEEE-CS (http://www.ieee-tcvlsi.org/) that endorses a league of successful meetings such as ARITH, ASAP, iSES, ISVLSI, etc., which are presented as “Sister Conferences”.

The following link has more details of these :

  • https://www.computer.org/web/tcvlsi/tcvlsi-sister-conferences.
